## Mandatory Restrictions

### 1. NO COMMERCIALIZATION

**YOU MUST NOT:**

‚ùå Sell this software or any derivative work
‚ùå Charge fees for access to this software
‚ùå Create paid tiers, editions, or versions
‚ùå Implement subscription or licensing models
‚ùå Bundle with paid products (unless this remains free)
‚ùå Charge for downloads, installations, or usage
‚ùå Monetize this software in ANY form

**This software MUST remain free.**

### 2. PERPETUAL FREE STATUS

Any modified or derivative version MUST:
- Remain under this license (or compatible)
- Stay free of charge forever
- Include this license in full
- Maintain attribution to BarrerSoftware

### 3. SERVICE EXCEPTION

You MAY charge for SERVICES, not SOFTWARE:

‚úÖ Technical support contracts
‚úÖ Installation and setup services
‚úÖ Training and education
‚úÖ Custom integration work
‚úÖ Consulting services

‚ùå The software itself must remain free

